&lt;p&gt;By simply knowing the proper url arguments, you can enable people to quickly save a Google Calendar event.
This example uses the Python standard: urllib to format the Google calendar url parameters and webbrowser to open the url in a browser. This is a handy little trick to keep in your back pocket!&lt;/p&gt;
